**Defense in Depth Layers**:

1. **Input Filtering Layer**:
```java
public class SSIInputValidator {

    private static final Set<String> BLOCKED_PATTERNS = Set.of(
        "<!--#", "<!", "#include", "#exec", "#echo",
        "#config", "#flastmod", "#fsize", "#printenv"
    );

    public static boolean isSafe(String input) {
        if (input == null) return true;

        String normalized = input.toLowerCase()
            .replace("%3c", "<")
            .replace("%3e", ">")
            .replace("%23", "#")
            .replace("%2d", "-");

        for (String pattern : BLOCKED_PATTERNS) {
            if (normalized.contains(pattern.toLowerCase())) {
                return false;
            }
        }
        return true;
    }
}
```

2. **Output Encoding Layer**:
```java
public class SSIOutputEncoder {

    public static String neutralizeSSI(String content) {
        // Replace SSI comment markers
        content = content.replace("<!--", "&lt;!--");
        content = content.replace("-->", "--&gt;");
        content = content.replace("#", "&#35;");
        return content;
    }
}
